Lint/UnusedMethodArgument.description:
Description

Checks for unused method arguments.
Lint/UnusedMethodArgument.option:
This rule supports the following parameters in your configuration:

AutoCorrect: contextual (type: str)
AllowUnusedKeywordArguments: False (type: bool)
IgnoreEmptyMethods: True (type: bool)
IgnoreNotImplementedMethods: True (type: bool)
NotImplementedExceptions: ['NotImplementedError'] (type: list)
